# Reproduce:  vhs docs/media/sdk-live.tape   (run from repo root)
Output docs/media/sdk-live-testnet.gif
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1200
Set Height 760
Set Padding 24
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 55ms
Hide
Type "cd sdk/typescript && clear"
Enter
Show
Sleep 600ms
Type "npm run example"
Enter
Sleep 16s
Sleep 2s
